Spotted in the wild! A new billboard was seen in New York for the upcoming movie "Michael," and the scale of it is absolutely legendary. The King of Pop is officially heading to the big screen, and seeing this pop up in the heart of the city makes the wait feel so much more real. Get ready to witness the greatness of
 a global icon. Can't wait to see this story unfold!

 @michaelmovie #Michaelin TheatersApril24th...

Lee Cronin's The Mummy, or simply The Mummy, is a 2026 American supernatural horror film written and directed by Lee Cronin. A reimagining of The Mummy franchise, the film stars Jack Reynor, Laia Costa, May Calamawy, Natalie Grace, and Verónica Falcón.

 James Wan and Jason Blum produce the film through their respective production banners, Atomic Monster and Blumhouse Productions, alongside Wicked/Good.

 @leecroninsthemummy #reels #explore #movie #horror #film

