Theo Von (@ theovon), a renowned American stand-up comedian and podcaster, has been making waves with his latest projects. Recently, he was named to Time magazine’s inaugural “TIME100 Creators” list, appearing in the “Leaders” category for his podcast This Past Weekend. Von has also been touring, with his 2025 tour dates selling out quickly, and is set to produce and star in a buddy comedy film called Busboys alongside David Spade 123 
