@fuze.film is a 2025 high-stakes heist thriller directed by David Mackenzie. The plot follows a daring group of thieves who use the discovery of an unexploded World War II bomb—and the resulting citywide evacuation—as cover for a bank robbery. Aaron Taylor-Johnson stars as a bomb disposal expert racing against time, while Theo James plays the mastermind behind the heist. The film is praised for its fast-paced moment
